{"tid":1578024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抵制黨鐵商場？唔使靠人多，只要整佢臭到生人勿近就得","createTime":"2019-09-18T03:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:03:52.000Z","uid":280412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec1e96d425657458b284a48dccc318c70e52e301","tid":1578024,"uid":280412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:34:12.000Z","msg":"我哋就算人再多，黨鐵商場啲舖最多咪落一日閘，咪當打多咗日風囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我哋應該改變策略，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>整臭佢，仲要臭到生人勿近</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n材料：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">臭魚罐頭/雞蛋</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n具體做法：大約50人約好一個時間，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">著街坊裝</span></strong></span>快閃是但一個黨鐵商場，定好喺同一時間將開咗嘅臭魚罐頭、打咗嘅蛋倒晒入商場嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">所有扶手梯罅位同升降機lift槽</span></strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要記住，倒落地清潔姐姐好快就可以清咗，但臭魚一旦被倒落扶手梯內膽同lift槽底/內壁，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵係極難搵出臭味源頭同清潔，更甚者啲汁液滲咗入扶手梯啲拆唔到嘅部件果陣，更可能要成條扶手梯報銷，到時可能冇一頭半個月都開唔返個場</span></strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，與其下下叫成千人出嚟，不如搵一小隊人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">認認真真玩一次臭魚</span></strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d236d6226b0e651894b2c7e5cca3691ac8d48738","tid":1578024,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:34:44.000Z","msg":"[未知算唔算文宣/輸出革命]戰區分法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n小弟出post想請大家過目"},{"pid":"66f94dba777f2d9f856b25592fa1429b2abb65fd","tid":1578024,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"臭魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人要戴口罩啦<br />\n(popo進場)<br />\n連藍絲都拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後藍轉黃,得咗"},{"pid":"11833bc8e1670ce4b1417f8bcb3c12a923e9e838","tid":1578024,"uid":280412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f94dba777f2d9f856b25592fa1429b2abb65fd","tid":1578024,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"臭魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人要戴口罩啦<br />\n(popo進場)<br />\n連藍絲都拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後藍轉黃,得咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"50人話去邊就去邊啦，一倒即閃，popo點會嚟得切呢？"},{"pid":"6f6d92b57d6a378a83bbb519fc699caaeedec6a5","tid":1578024,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11833bc8e1670ce4b1417f8bcb3c12a923e9e838","tid":1578024,"uid":280412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f94dba777f2d9f856b25592fa1429b2abb65fd","tid":1578024,"uid":305009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"臭魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人要戴口罩啦<br />\n(popo進場)<br />\n連藍絲都拉埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig